Sentencas: La-coating by electron-beam vacuum deposition was applied to a chromia-forming alloy.
Titulo: Oxidation behavior of an La-coated chromia-forming alloy and the electrical property of oxide scales

Sentencas: The effects of La-coating on oxidation behavior of the alloy and on the electrical property of the oxide scale, thermally grown in solid oxide fuel cell (SOFC) operating atmospheres, were investigated.
Titulo: Oxidation behavior of an La-coated chromia-forming alloy and the electrical property of oxide scales

Sentencas: The elemental analysis results of La-coated specimens indicate that chromium in the alloy is oxidized internally under the La-diffusion region.
Titulo: Oxidation behavior of an La-coated chromia-forming alloy and the electrical property of oxide scales

Sentencas: The electric resistance of the La-coated specimen is found to be lower than that of the uncoated specimen by more than one order of magnitude.
Titulo: Oxidation behavior of an La-coated chromia-forming alloy and the electrical property of oxide scales
